  },
  {
    "channel_id": "chan-002",
    "content": "Pulled the bus route times. The proposed Sage Creek consolidation would put some kids on a 45-minute one-way ride. That's the number we keep coming back to.",
    "content_type": "text",
    "created_date": "2026-02-03T18:30:00Z",
